code: @Override public void execute() {     BatchGetItemResult result = ddbClient.batchGetItem(new BatchGetItemRequest().withRequestItems(determineBatchItems())).     Map tmp = new HashMap<>().     tmp.put(DdbConstants.BATCH_RESPONSE, result.getResponses()).     tmp.put(DdbConstants.UNPROCESSED_KEYS, result.getUnprocessedKeys()).     addToResults(tmp). }
@SuppressWarnings("unchecked") private Map<String, KeysAndAttributes> determineBatchItems() {     return exchange.getIn().getHeader(DdbConstants.BATCH_ITEMS, Map.class). }
